<p>Villu moves from Skype to become the new <a href="http://www.hillandknowlton.ee/?id=128&amp;lang=en" title="Hill &#038; Knowlton">CEO of Hill &amp; Knowlton Estonia</a>. Filling his shoes in the blogging role will be a challenge, but one I&rsquo;m very much looking forward to.</p>
